Movie Name: The Man Who Cheated Himself

A 1950 crime film noir directed by Felix E. Feist, and starring Lee J. Cobb, Jane Wyatt and John Dall. A cops girlfriend shoots the husband she is divorcing, and the cop tries to cover it up. But, then his hotshot younger brother is assigned to the case.
